# Business Brain™ Memory & Retrieval (Spec 117)

**Full document:** `docs/SPARK_BUSINESS_BRAIN_MEMORY_RETRIEVAL_FRAMEWORK.md`

**Trust layer:** [Spec 112 Companion Memory](./SPARK_COMPANION_MEMORY_CONTEXT_FRAMEWORK.md) — wins on persist conflicts

**OS:** [003 Business Brain](../spark-intelligence-foundation/003-business-brain.md) · [009 Lifecycle](../spark-intelligence-foundation/009-business-brain-lifecycle.md) · [007 MVC](../spark-intelligence-foundation/007-context-strategy.md)

## Core principle

Brain is a **living map** — not a database, not a folder tree.

## Seven questions (this spec answers all)

Remember · Connect · Organize without folders · Retrieve naturally · Avoid duplicates · Recognize patterns · Forget what doesn't matter

## Remembering pipeline

Signal → **Trust gate (112)** → Classify → Lifecycle → Connect → Permission → Active

Never learn from single utterance alone unless member confirms. Writes async — never block conversation.

## Connect ideas (not folders)

1. **Lineage** — `originatedFromId` / `originatedFromKind`
2. **LIG** — `connectionIds` (evolved_from, supports, supersedes, pattern_of…)
3. **Asset anchors** — knowledge belongs to living Business Assets™

## Organize without folders

Member sees: Companion Boxes™ · Business Assets™ · Projects · Memory Center™

Invisible: Living Intelligence Graph · category × freshness × lifecycle clustering

## Retrieve naturally

Brain stores; **Context Strategy selects MVC** — never load entire Brain.

Rank: lifecycle × freshness × relevance × confidence.

Check Brain **before re-asking**. Hospitality language from Spec 112.

Observed/Candidate → never assert as fact. Active/Mature → recall naturally.

## Avoid duplicates

Entity resolution on canonical keys + asset anchors + lineage.

Same fact → strengthen. Business evolution → **version** (preserve history). Competing → hold + confirm.

Evolution = one lineage chain — not copies.

## Patterns (ethical)

Observations only — never identity labels, shame, or unprompted lectures.

Separate pattern records; tentative confidence; surface only when relevant.

## Forgetting

Ignore session chatter · Decay unreinforced candidates · Archive completed · Historical superseded · Retire on delete

Spec 112 lists what **never** becomes durable.

**Wiser, not larger.**

## Boundaries

Brain: store · connect · retrieve · propose writes

Brain never: member copy · recommendations · UI · bypass permission

